  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 1em;margin-right: 1em;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjjsqoz0ygv\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503048950\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6666666666666666\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1536\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b579f7e9&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FrwnawOsSCFrzQl53TW2884M1viaPj7JibaRmiaffcnUBS2AMXKFjU6YcFaQV2gtpMUglYpd0MiaY8l8ju8eia8iarJcw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 1em;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjjsqoz0lup\"><font color=\"#A5A5A5\"><span style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjjrz8cb1nn5\"><span style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mjjsmj1e1olk\" style=\"font-size: 12px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">出品｜网易科技《态度》</span></span></span></span></font></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 1em;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjjsqoz0p2c\"><font color=\"#A5A5A5\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:12px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjjsmj1ek5u\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">作者｜袁宁</span></span></font></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 1em;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjjsqoz01sqo\"><font color=\"#A5A5A5\"><span style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjjrz8cb1ye\"><span style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);font-size: 12px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjjsmj1e153v\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">编辑｜丁广胜</span></span></span></span></font></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 1em;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjjsqoz0agv\"><font color=\"#A5A5A5\"></font></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 1em;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjjsqoz01kh9\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjjrz8cb1jn\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);\">大模型的故事讲了三年，终于到了要“交卷”的时刻。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 1em;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjjsqoz0kus\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjjrz8cb1e6b\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);\">短短48小时内，MiniMax与智谱两家独角兽接连递表，争夺“全球大模型第一股”。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 1em;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjjsqoz01vqo\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjjrz8cb1agl\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);\">随着招股书的披露，真实的营收、亏损与现金流数据，将这两家昔日的“概念独角兽”还原为具体的商业实体。我们首次能以精确的数据颗粒度，审视中国两家头部大模型公司的真实成色。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 1em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjjsqoz010j8\"><font color=\"#C00000\"></font></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 1em;margin-right: 1em;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjjsqoz0lc9\"><img data-imgfileid=\"502851486\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.15204678362573099\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"684\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=068d1b16&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FrwnawOsSCFp4iatBAbsJzvVraDq6Xh5OHp8QJSvdPzF1icMb5w3x1Umm9iblCmmT5TicezNBeKzhc5teZXS1PElhxw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 1em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjjsqoz0egz\"><font color=\"#C00000\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mjjrz8cb7qv\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-size:20px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjjs00ky19cd\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjjs00lemke\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">两种路径：</span></span></span></font></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 1em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjjsqoz017f4\"><font color=\"#C00000\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mjjrz8cb7qv\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-size:20px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjjs00ky19cd\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjjs00lemke\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">To B的厚重与To C的轻盈</span></span></span></font></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 1em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjjsqoz013aw\"><font color=\"#C00000\"></font></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 1em;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjjsqoz01f6r\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mjjrz8cbp6i\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);\">智谱与MiniMax，恰好代表了中国大模型商业化的两种路径</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">：</span></span><strong inline-dir=\"ltr\" ql-global=\"true\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">一个向左走To B/G做“重”，一个向右走To C出海做“轻”。</span></span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 1em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjjsqoz02043\"><span inline-dir=\"ltr\" ql-global=\"true\" mpa-font-style=\"mjjrz8cb1rzh\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">先看营收规模与结构。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 1em;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjjsqoz0fc\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjjrz8cb1gay\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);\">招股书数据显示，智谱的增长曲线极为陡峭，2024年收入达到3.124亿元人民币，三年复合增长率高达130%。根据弗若斯特沙利文报告，以2024年收入计，智谱是中国最大的独立大模型厂商。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 1em;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjjsqoz0gkw\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjjrz8cb1iex\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);\">但从其收入结构来看，“传统”色彩极强：截至2025年6月30日，84.8%的收入来自私有化部署，主要服务于政府与大型企业。虽然MaaS（云端API）收入在增长，但目前仅占15.2%。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 1em;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjjsqoz0xcz\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjjrz8cbo1k\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);\">这意味着，智谱的大部分收入，并非来自性感的“云端API调用”，而是来自一个个具体的、甚至定制化的项目。这像极了软件外包的逻辑：虽有50%以上的毛利，却难以摆脱“堆人头、做交付”的重资产属性。智谱不仅要卖模型，还得卖服务、卖实施。</span></span></p>\n  <figure style=\"margin-left: 1em;margin-right: 1em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjjsqoz011ri\">\n   <p style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-top:0px;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503048947\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"750\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;vertical-align: middle;background: none transparent;min-height: unset;object-fit: contain;width: 702.031px;height: auto;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b04bc034&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FrwnawOsSCFrzQl53TW2884M1viaPj7JibaaJAn8u9Jdwkx0zX1BDDVe16QpJkL3uobIxWJOs8JmjqibGj4P1ib0qEQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dother%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  </figure>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 1em;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjjsqoz02uu\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:12px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjjsmvhuqqg\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjjsmviaa6j\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">（图注：智谱各项表现，来自MiniMax招股书）</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 1em;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjjsqoz0917\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mjjrz8cbgq0\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><strong inline-dir=\"ltr\" ql-global=\"true\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">另一边，MiniMax则走向了另一个极端。</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);\">其2025年前9个月的收入达到5343.7万美元（约3.8亿人民币），且超过70%的收入来自海外。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 1em;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjjsqoz023wv\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjjrz8cboj3\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);\">不同于智谱的“项目制”，MiniMax靠的是Talkie等AI原生应用，这是一种更符合互联网爆发逻辑的模式——C端产品驱动，用户量（MAU）接近2800万。</span></span></p>\n  <figure style=\"margin-left: 1em;margin-right: 1em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjjsqoz01bka\">\n   <p style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-top:0px;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503048946\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.584\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"750\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;vertical-align: middle;background: none transparent;min-height: unset;object-fit: contain;width: 702.031px;height: auto;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=763a7b77&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FrwnawOsSCFrzQl53TW2884M1viaPj7Jiba3NIbHIBfPFxymAgtRv3NGGtrNEKFGnWYib6FEPj8BkGTN2d6wppfraA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dother%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  </figure>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 1em;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjjsqoz013el\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:12px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjjsnbb420iu\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjjsnbbkp4j\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">（图注：MiniMax的收入数据摘要，来自MiniMax招股书）</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 1em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjjsqoz01c4s\"><span inline-dir=\"ltr\" ql-global=\"true\" mpa-font-style=\"mjjrz8cb1ddy\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">再来看盈利能力与成本控制。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 1em;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjjsqoz01yrq\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mjjrz8cb1vhs\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);\">数据显示，智谱AI的毛利率长期维持在</span></span><strong ql-global=\"true\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">50%以上</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);\">这得益于其私有化部署的定价权，但也暗示了其交付成本的刚性——做项目，总是要堆人的。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 1em;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjjsqoz05y8\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mjjrz8cbqno\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><strong inline-dir=\"ltr\" ql-global=\"true\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">MiniMax展现出的毛利率修复速度与“省钱”能力则更值得注意</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);font-weight: bold;\">。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);\">从2023年的负毛利，到2025年前9个月转正为23.3%，也一定程度上证明了C端推理成本是可以被规模化效应摊薄的。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 1em;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjjsqoz01mky\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjjrz8cb14ep\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);\">此外，MiniMax从成立至今累计花费约5亿美元，相当于仅用OpenAI约1%的资金，就做出了全球领先的多模态模型。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 1em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjjsqoz01noa\"><span inline-dir=\"ltr\" ql-global=\"true\" mpa-font-style=\"mjjrz8cb1126\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">最后看研发和亏损。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 1em;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjjsqoz01yy4\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjjrz8cb14dk\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);\">无论模式如何，亏损是共同的底色。智谱2024年经调整净亏损约29.58亿元，MiniMax同期亏损3.48亿美元。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 1em;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjjsqoz022dy\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjjrz8cb7wp\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);\">巨额亏损的源头只有一个：算力。智谱2024年研发投入高达21.9亿元，几乎是营收的7倍。截至2025年中，智谱拥有657名研发人员，占公司总员工数的74%。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 1em;margin-right: 1em;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjjsqoz080r\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"503048951\" data-ratio=\"0.9380403458213257\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1388\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=483cc178&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FrwnawOsSCFrzQl53TW2884M1viaPj7JibaXeFI2ebx4iavWr6ibV0ITUCFLc3raL72obfdgvnuibqfKpYkHSaic3gsRA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 1em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjjsqoz01zuk\"><span inline-dir=\"ltr\" ql-global=\"true\" mpa-font-style=\"mjjrz8cb1la9\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><font color=\"#C00000\"></font></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 1em;margin-right: 1em;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjjsqoz0u2u\"><img data-imgfileid=\"502851485\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.15204678362573099\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"684\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b32c57a5&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FrwnawOsSCFp4iatBAbsJzvVraDq6Xh5OHe8dmhZIvx7iacyxC16ia2UjD7RPRrHRnpI5hPAqMqiaNcFDlXwVhCTZvQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 1em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjjsqoz019hr\"><span inline-dir=\"ltr\" ql-global=\"true\" mpa-font-style=\"mjjrz8cb1la9\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><font color=\"#C00000\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-size:20px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjjsf9m4yt6\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjjsf9mkqn2\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">一种焦虑：</span></span></font></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 1em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjjsqoz0f70\"><span inline-dir=\"ltr\" ql-global=\"true\" mpa-font-style=\"mjjrz8cb1la9\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><font color=\"#C00000\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-size:20px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjjsf9m4yt6\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjjsf9mkqn2\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">烧钱无底洞与脆弱的护城河</span></span></font></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 1em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjjsqoz0pw1\"><span inline-dir=\"ltr\" ql-global=\"true\" mpa-font-style=\"mjjrz8cb1la9\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><font color=\"#C00000\"></font></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 1em;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjjsqoz020p4\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjjrz8cb5ya\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);\">招股书虽然展示了增长，但也暴露了这两家公司，乃至整个行业面临的深层困境。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 1em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjjsqoz02th\"><span inline-dir=\"ltr\" ql-global=\"true\" mpa-font-style=\"mjjrz8cb15g\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">首先是商业模式层面。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 1em;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjjsqoz02527\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjjrz8cb12r2\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);\">从两家的现状来看，目前的商业化进程，远未跑通“研发投入-收入增长-利润覆盖”的闭环。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 1em;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjjsqoz01xzp\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mjjrz8cbf05\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><strong inline-dir=\"ltr\" ql-global=\"true\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">智谱的困境在于“做不轻”</span></span></strong><strong ql-global=\"true\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">。</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);\">私有化部署虽然现金流稳定，但本质是项目制，难以像SaaS那样指数级扩张。且客户集中度极高，2024年最大客户贡献了19%的收入，一旦大客户流失，业绩将剧烈波动。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 1em;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjjsqoz01j2q\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mjjrz8cb14rm\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><strong inline-dir=\"ltr\" ql-global=\"true\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">MiniMax的困境则在于</span></span></strong><strong ql-global=\"true\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">“留不住”</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);\">C端产品极度依赖爆款，用户喜新厌旧速度极快。且随着用户规模扩大，推理成本线性上升，并没有传统互联网软件“边际成本为零”的红利。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 1em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjjsqoz01zzf\"><span inline-dir=\"ltr\" ql-global=\"true\" mpa-font-style=\"mjjrz8cb197n\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">其次，开源模型是悬在头顶的达摩克利斯之剑。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 1em;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjjsqoz0i87\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjjrz8cb15t2\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);\">随着DeepSeek、Qwen等高性能开源模型的涌现，大模型的“稀缺性”正在迅速瓦解。当顶尖的智力变成像水电一样的廉价商品，智谱和MiniMax依靠模型能力赚取的溢价空间将被无限压缩。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 1em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjjsqoz0ilh\"><span inline-dir=\"ltr\" ql-global=\"true\" mpa-font-style=\"mjjrz8cbsu5\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">此外，地缘与合规的“双重枷锁”也是隐忧。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 1em;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjjsqoz04ja\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjjrz8cb1c2a\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);\">智谱在招股书中特意提到了“供应链安全”，在芯片受限的背景下，如何持续推进AGI研发是巨大的不确定性。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 1em;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjjsqoz0214z\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjjrz8cb1c2a\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);\">而MiniMax则面临“出海风险”，70%收入来自海外，一旦面临类似TikTok的监管压力，或者与迪士尼等巨头的版权诉讼爆发，其商业根基将面临严峻挑战。</span></span></p>\n  <figure style=\"margin-left: 1em;margin-right: 1em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjjsqoz0ntw\">\n   <p style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-top:0px;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"503048948\" data-ratio=\"0.308\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;vertical-align: middle;background: none transparent;min-height: unset;object-fit: contain;width: 702.031px;height: auto;\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"750\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=dd59c1ab&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FrwnawOsSCFrzQl53TW2884M1viaPj7JibalFLqfffhb0KHFiaYRrS5tapjic9fR1oMKPueLthqQHv5nlYyu2jUkcpg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dother%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  </figure>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 1em;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjjsqoz0102s\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:12px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjjsorqf1c5v\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjjsorqv1fgh\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">（图注：来自智谱招股书）</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 1em;margin-right: 1em;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjjsqoz0uoz\"><img data-imgfileid=\"502851487\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.15204678362573099\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"684\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=79f3dc0f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FrwnawOsSCFp4iatBAbsJzvVraDq6Xh5OHdOIEqSz20g8o4dAYA8BG95LnFdpwSFP2h87ospwfaTyzzpjcxMFR0w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 1em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjjsqoz112cu\"><span inline-dir=\"ltr\" ql-global=\"true\" mpa-font-style=\"mjjrz8cb1uu9\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><font color=\"#C00000\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-size:20px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjjsi1pt1rkc\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjjsi1qb1qj1\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">上市即“上岸”？</span></span></font></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 1em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjjsqoz1zoi\"><span inline-dir=\"ltr\" ql-global=\"true\" mpa-font-style=\"mjjrz8cb1uu9\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><font color=\"#C00000\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-size:20px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjjsi1pt1rkc\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjjsi1qb1qj1\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">中场战事才刚刚开始</span></span></font></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin: 0px 1em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjjsqoz1epk\"><span inline-dir=\"ltr\" ql-global=\"true\" mpa-font-style=\"mjjrz8cb1uu9\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><font color=\"#C00000\"></font></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 1em;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjjsqoz121b\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjjrz8cbwjc\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);\">IPO只是开始，真正的考验在于上市后的“造血”能力。结合行业最新的动态，接下来的剧本，可能会这样演：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 1em;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjjsqoz1219j\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mjjrz8cb23aa\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><strong inline-dir=\"ltr\" ql-global=\"true\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">第一，估值体系的重构。</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);\">市场将不再单纯为“技术梦想”买单。智谱和MiniMax的上市，将为行业确立一个锚点。如果二级市场对这两家公司的亏损容忍度低，那么整个一级市场的大模型估值逻辑都将重改。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 1em;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjjsqoz11tth\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mjjrz8cb1qdp\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><strong inline-dir=\"ltr\" ql-global=\"true\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">第二，洗牌加速。</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);\">上市只是开始，二级市场的资金是极其挑剔的。一旦财报无法持续兑现增长预期，股价的惩罚将比一级市场的融资失败更为惨烈。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 1em;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjjsqoz122vb\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mjjrz8cb1o6d\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><strong inline-dir=\"ltr\" ql-global=\"true\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">其中还有一点值得注意，是中国式效率的“红利”。</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);\">&nbsp;MiniMax的数据透露出一个积极信号：中国公司在模型工程化上的效率极高。算力成本占比的大幅下降（从收入的13倍降至2倍多），意味着在应用层，中国公司或许能比OpenAI更快跑通盈利模型。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 1em;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjjsqoz116da\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mjjrz8cb136p\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);\">大模型的中场战事已经打响。对于智谱和MiniMax而言，递交招股书的那一刻，它们就从“被仰望的神坛”，走进了“被审视的斗兽场”。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 1em;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mjjsqoz11dm3\"><em inline-dir=\"ltr\" ql-global=\"true\" mpa-font-style=\"mjjrz8cb1gql\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><span style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);letter-spacing: 1.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">注：题图由AI生成；本文数据援引自智谱、MiniMax公开招股书。</span></span></span></em></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "本文通过分析 MiniMax 和智谱的招股书，拆解了两家中国头部大模型公司 To B/G 与 To C 两种商业模式的优劣、巨大的算力成本、行业面临的困境及未来的发展预判。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "本文通过分析 MiniMax 和智谱的招股书，拆解了两家中国头部大模型公司 To B/G 与 To C 两种商业模式的优劣、巨大的算力成本、行业面临的困境及未来的发展预判。",
  "summary": "本文深度剖析了中国两大头部大模型公司 MiniMax 和智谱的商业模式、财务状况、面临的挑战及未来发展趋势。通过对两家公司招股书数据的解读，文章指出智谱 AI 主要走 To B/G 的“私有化部署”重资产路线，营收增长快但模式较重，毛利率较高但伴随“堆人头做交付”成本；而 MiniMax 则侧重 To C 海外市场，通过 AI 原生应用实现快速收入增长与毛利率修复，但 C 端产品对爆款依赖高且推理成本随用户规模线性上升。文章还揭示了两公司共同面临的巨额亏损源于算力投入，以及整个行业在商业模式未跑通、开源模型冲击、地缘政治与合规风险下的深层困境。最后，文章预判大模型行业将面临估值体系重构和洗牌加速，但中国公司在模型工程化上的效率或能率先跑通盈利模式。",
